CASE → Used for performance categories (Excellent, Average, Needs Improvement) and others  

AVG() → To calculate student/subject average marks  

COUNT() → For attendance statistics  

Views → Created student_dashboard view.  

##Queries:  

#1. Student Average Performance Report  
#2. Subject-Wise Class Performance  
#3. Attendance Percentage per Student  
#4. View for Dashboard Reporting  
